174
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:53,100
Cheers!

175
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:53,999
Together!

176
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:54,900
Happy New Year!

177
00:12:54,901 --> 00:12:56,480
Together!

