589
00:41:13,200 --> 00:41:17,099
My friend is not my friend.

590
00:41:20,300 --> 00:41:21,800
Fine.

591
00:41:23,200 --> 00:41:24,600
Fine!

592
00:41:32,700 --> 00:41:34,750
